 isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/real-estate/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-israels-real-estate-market-rising-prices-are-over-not-everyone-has-grasped-that/0000018f-118a-d2e1-a7df-11ae791f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端正统社区的城市更新？情况很复杂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/real-estate/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/urban-renewal-for-israels-ultra-orthodox-neighborhoods-its-complicated/0000018f-1175-df8a-afcf-bf7fb9440000</link><description>在以色列各地的极端正统社区，拉比们站出来反对城市重建项目，他们认为这些项目对居民构成威胁，导致社区成员住在老旧、不安全的房屋中，整个社区面临严重的住房短缺。但潮流可能正在慢慢转变</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 13:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/real-estate/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/urban-renewal-for-israels-ultra-orthodox-neighborhoods-its-complicated/0000018f-1175-df8a-afcf-bf7fb9440000</guid></item><item><title>“相互尊重”：这些宗教和世俗的以色列人选择生活在一起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/real-estate/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-this-community-religious-and-secular-israelis-live-together-by-choice/0000018f-107a-df8a-afcf-bf7b2fd10000</link><description>当信教的妻子和世俗的丈夫找不到合适的社区时，他们就建立了一个社区。现在，他们的基布兹社区证明了不同宗教信仰的人们可以住在一起</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 13:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/real-estate/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-this-community-religious-and-secular-israelis-live-together-by-choice/0000018f-107a-df8a-afcf-bf7b2fd10000</guid></item><item><title>报道：哈马斯接受加沙停火协议；以色列官员否认战争结束的前景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article/.premium/report-hamas-accepts-gaza-cease-fire-deal-israeli-officials-deny-prospect-of-war-ending/0000018f-42eb-d414-a5bf-f3fff18a0000</link><description>据报道，哈马斯得到了美国的保证，以色列将全面撤出加沙地带，并且一旦人质获释，以色列军队将不会继续战斗。 一名以色列官员告诉《国土报》，“以色列在任何情况下都不会同意作为协议的一部分结束战争并决心进入拉法</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 11:02:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article/.premium/report-hamas-accepts-gaza-cease-fire-deal-israeli-officials-deny-prospect-of-war-ending/0000018f-42eb-d414-a5bf-f3fff18a0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：如果哈马斯领导人拒绝加沙停火协议，美国要求卡塔尔驱逐他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article/.premium/report-u-s-deamnds-qatar-to-expel-hamas-leaders-if-they-refuse-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-426d-d91a-a5af-e3fd50c10000</link><description>报道补充说，美国国务卿布林肯上个月向卡塔尔首相传达了这一信息。哈马斯高级官员告诉国土报，以色列和美国致力于停火，但目前尚不清楚以色列是否会在人质获释后恢复战斗</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 08:32:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article/.premium/report-u-s-deamnds-qatar-to-expel-hamas-leaders-if-they-refuse-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-426d-d91a-a5af-e3fd50c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队空袭，围困约旦河西岸武装分子建筑；五名巴勒斯坦人被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article-live/report-u-s-tells-qatar-to-expel-hamas-leaders-if-they-refuse-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-412e-d17f-adcf-f9eff5aa0000</link><description>报道：美国要求卡塔尔驱逐哈马斯领导人，如果他们拒绝加沙停火协议 ■ 沙特媒体报道，哈马斯将在未来几小时内接受埃及的停火协议 ■ 埃及消息人士称，中央情报局局长将在开罗参加有关加沙冲突的会议 ■ 以色列向哈马斯提出问题在入侵拉法之前达成为期一周的最后通牒 ■ 联合国世界粮食计划署主任称加沙北部正处于“全面饥荒”</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 01:42:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article-live/report-u-s-tells-qatar-to-expel-hamas-leaders-if-they-refuse-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-412e-d17f-adcf-f9eff5aa0000</guid></item><item><title>在约旦河西岸，甚至救护车也无法幸免于以色列军队的致命炮火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-west-bank-not-even-ambulances-are-immune-to-israeli-army-gunfire/0000018f-3b2a-d17f-adcf-fbeb03630000</link><description>一名载着两名伤员前往约旦河西岸医院的巴勒斯坦救护车司机被以色列军队开枪打死。在以色列国防军在加沙杀害数百名医务人员后，士兵们毫不犹豫地在其他地方也犯下了这种严重违反刑法的行为。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 22:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-west-bank-not-even-ambulances-are-immune-to-israeli-army-gunfire/0000018f-3b2a-d17f-adcf-fbeb03630000</guid></item><item><title>“突然我意识到我在燃烧”：在加沙作战的以色列人分享他们的所见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/suddenly-i-realize-that-im-burning-israelis-who-fought-in-gaza-share-what-they-saw/0000018f-3fe6-d91a-a5af-bff7ce220000</link><description>加沙战场归来的八名以色列士兵的独白</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 21:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/suddenly-i-realize-that-im-burning-israelis-who-fought-in-gaza-share-what-they-saw/0000018f-3fe6-d91a-a5af-bff7ce220000</guid></item><item><title>据信在加沙被扣为人质的以色列人于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体在以色列坟墓中被发现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-believed-to-be-hostage-in-gaza-killed-on-oct-7-body-found-in-grave-in-israel/0000018f-3f71-d516-afbf-fff329b90000</link><description>哈马斯突然袭击以色列南部 210 天后，埃利亚基姆·利布曼 (Elyakim Libman) 的家人收到消息称他被谋杀，并没有像之前想象的那样被带到加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 19:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-believed-to-be-hostage-in-gaza-killed-on-oct-7-body-found-in-grave-in-israel/0000018f-3f71-d516-afbf-fff329b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长威胁摧毁巴勒斯坦权力机构是内塔尼亚胡最新的愚蠢举动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-threat-to-destroy-the-palestinian-authority-is-his-latest-asinine-antic/0000018f-3ea6-d414-a5bf-bfb7327e0000</link><description>以色列具体将如何做到这一点？一旦巴勒斯坦权力机构解散，谁将控制西岸？没有什么比以色列拒绝支持甚至拒绝接受乔·拜登的该地区计划更愚蠢的了</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-threat-to-destroy-the-palestinian-authority-is-his-latest-asinine-antic/0000018f-3ea6-d414-a5bf-bfb7327e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 210 天：据报道，以色列给哈马斯一周时间，以便在拉法行动之前达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-210-israel-reportedly-gives-hamas-week-to-make-deal-before-rafah-op/0000018f-3f49-d516-afbf-ffcb4b7b0000</link><description>英国宣布对四名以色列定居者实施制裁，该组织是极右翼组织，对约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人实施暴力行为。 ■ 据报道，以色列通知哈马斯，如果人质协议在一周内得不到落实，它将袭击拉法。加沙永久停火 ■ 战争进入 210 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:39:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-210-israel-reportedly-gives-hamas-week-to-make-deal-before-rafah-op/0000018f-3f49-d516-afbf-ffcb4b7b0000</guid></item><item><title>英国对参与西岸暴力事件的以色列极端组织和四名定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/u-k-sanctions-extremist-israeli-group-four-settlers-involved-in-west-bank-violence/0000018f-3edf-d516-afbf-fedf0bda0000</link><description>受到英国制裁的四名以色列右翼人士是伊利沙·耶里德（Elisha Yered）、诺姆·费德曼（Noam Federman）、内里亚·本·帕齐（Neriya Ben Pazi）和伊登·利维（Eden Levy）</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:02:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/u-k-sanctions-extremist-israeli-group-four-settlers-involved-in-west-bank-violence/0000018f-3edf-d516-afbf-fedf0bda0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚曾经是以色列人的梦想学校。现在他们成了校园贱民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-used-to-be-a-dream-school-for-israelis-now-theyre-campus-pariahs/0000018f-3dcb-d0b5-a59f-3dcfd8cf0000</link><description>许多人认为，位于美国校园亲巴勒斯坦团结运动最前沿的哥伦比亚大学的加沙抗议活动并不是反犹太主义的。很难声称他们不针对以色列人</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 13:34:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-used-to-be-a-dream-school-for-israelis-now-theyre-campus-pariahs/0000018f-3dcb-d0b5-a59f-3dcfd8cf0000</gui