-3de3-d8f8-abbf-7fe39b8d0000</link><description>周二，内塔尼亚胡称以色列军事和政治官员因在加沙犯下的罪行而受到逮捕令的可能性是“反犹太仇恨犯罪”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/icc-prosecutor-work-undermined-by-threats-as-netanyahu-army-brass-face-arrest-warrants/0000018f-3de3-d8f8-abbf-7fe39b8d0000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易和拉法攻势达到临界点，以色列可能会崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-and-rafah-op-reach-tipping-point-and-israel-could-fall-either-way/0000018f-3a0e-d0b5-a59f-3bcf9a540000</link><description>人质交易陷入了内塔尼亚胡的“岩石”和辛瓦尔的“困境”之间，全世界都在等待哈马斯对当前提议的答复。彻底的胜利”被认为是</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-and-rafah-op-reach-tipping-point-and-israel-could-fall-either-way/0000018f-3a0e-d0b5-a59f-3bcf9a540000</guid></item></channel></rss>